author: Associated Press
description: Aaron Hernandez's fiancee Shayanna Jenkins-Hernandez says former tight end thought he was soon to be released from prison.

author: Eliott C. McLaughlin, CNN
description: The fiancee of former New England Patriot Aaron Hernandez doesn't believe her high school sweetheart committed murder or suicide, she said in a prerecorded television interview that aired Monday.
title: Aaron Hernandez's fiancee: 'I don't think this was a suicide'

description: Aaron Hernandez's fiancee, Shayanna Jenkins-Hernandez, says she doesn't think his death in his prison cell on April 19 was a suicide.
title: Hernandez's fiancee casts doubt on his suicide

title: Shayanna Jenkins-Hernandez goes on Dr. Phil; Celtics Win! 5-15-2017
